    "description": "Leave your normal routine behind and start a journey with no fixed destination. Choose a direction and go \u2014 by foot, bike, or train \u2014 but don\u2019t plan the outcome. During your quest, you must complete three objectives: 1. Discover something unexpected Find a place you didn\u2019t plan to visit. It can be small, but it must feel like a real discovery. 2. The Mind Checkpoint Sit down alone for 10\u201315 minutes. Think about one real thing in your life: what you want, what bothers you, or what you would change. 3. Do one uncomfortable action Step out of your comfort zone. Talk to someone, take a random path, or try something new. Rules: \u2022 No social media during the quest \u2022 Minimal music (max. 10 minutes) \u2022 Make spontaneous decisions only End the quest at a calm place (sunset if possible) and reflect: \u201cWas I more myself today than usual?\u201d",
