    "title": "\u201cGuys, I swear I have a girlfriend!\u201d",
    "description": "This quest is not recommended for normal quest takers. This quest is quite simple but also very taxing on the mind. Step one: Claim you have a girlfriend to your friends, then let that simmer for a bit until people start asking, \u201cWho and where is she? How do you know her?\u201d That kind of jazz. The problem is, you can\u2019t show what they look like or their social media, because they don\u2019t exist. There is no real second step, because you just have to BS it until too many people start guessing. Make up as many random facts as possible to make it believable, but also add some wrong facts so the smarter people start realizing something\u2019s wrong. When someone asks you about it, deny it with all your will. Adamantly deny everyone who tries to dig into the lie until the very end, where you reveal this quest to one or two people. This is difficult to do because it\u2019s a lie people will try and use the internet to debunk. If you are forced to give a name, make up something simple. WARNING: THIS IS NOT RECOMMENDED, FOR IT MAY RUIN MANY FRIENDSHIPS. ONLY DO THIS IF YOU REALLY, REALLY ARE BORED. THIS IS YOUR LAST WARNING.",
